      "details": "\n            \n        <div class=\"card-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"row hmr-6\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 mt-2\">\n                    <h2 class=\"jobtitle mb-1 pb-1\">Join Liberty's Sales Force</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <h2 class=\"opportunity-company mb-1 pb-1\">Liberty Financial Advisers</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <div class=\"card-detail-meta mt-0\">\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-geo-pin-solid\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Location: </strong>North West, North West</p>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-calendar-event-solid\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Date posted:</strong> 17 November 2023</p>\n                            </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <h6 class=\"opportunity-reference mb-3 mt-3\">Reference number: 4438359173</h6>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col text-break\">\n                            <h2>Role description</h2>\n                            <p class=\"text-break white-space-pre-line\">Liberty is expanding our Salesforce Does this appeal to you. Be your own boss? Manage your own time? Write your own pay cheque? Enjoy socializing and networking with people? If your answer is yes to any of these questions, dont delay. Apply now Join Liberty now, a market leader in the Financial Services sector and start your career as a Professional Financial Advisor Join this exciting career and have the opportunity to establish your own brand within the Liberty banner. We at Liberty all have one thing in common and that is achieving our goals and successes, from our clients to our employees. Our Financial Advisors are put through a thorough on-boarding process with quality training to make sure that our clients get the quality and best possible service to reach their financial goals and aspirations. Ongoing learning and development are what keeps us in the running. You as a Financial Advisor will be required to meet with clients daily, prospecting and analysing what they need to obtain their goals and advise on the best possible way to achieve them. Building trust and ongoing relationships with these clients. You will Identify new business opportunities and develop and Implement strategies and manage individual and corporate relationships. What we are looking for: a Team player with the ability to function independently Experienced individual with a track record in high performance sales environments Has a network in which they can attract and source both individual and corporate clients Strong sales, interpersonal and business development skills, and acumen Strong communication skills Strong Business acumen and analytical skills Strong Sales acumen Entrepreneurial mindset Minimum Candidate Requirements: National Senior Certificate Clear credit record Clear criminal record Valid drivers licence (compulsory) Own reliable transport (compulsory) Own laptop and strong internet connection What we offer: Support from a network of proficient professionals committed to helping you succeed. Learning and Development Benefits Excellent commission structure Comprehensive training program and on-going mentoring and learning that will provide you with the knowledge and skills to be successful in this enviroment. Send your cv to Janeen.jordaanliberty.co.za</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <hr>\n                            <p class=\"disclaimer\">Please note, you'll be redirected to an external site that will use your mobile data.</p>\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col\">\n                                    <yth-button-group class=\"start hydrated\" alignment=\"start\">\n                                        <yth-button-legacy auto-click-loader=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/View/OpportunityApplyExternal?tracker=MQAxADkAMAA2ADUAMwAxADgAMQA&amp;externalurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adzuna.co.za%2Fland%2Fad%2F4438359173%3Fv%3DA8907F177A35286F762ED98BC37E4FDA882EF69C%26ccd%3D2ff00162fcaefe93a42a16b464fa1942%26frd%3Da245ae3a07ce3064296d085176c0f2a0%26r%3D14906411%26utm_source%3Dharambee%26utm_medium%3Dppc%26partnerb%3D1%26chnlid%3D1782%26a%3De\" variant=\"primary\" theme=\"standard\" size=\"regular\" class=\"hydrated\">\n                                            Apply now\n                                        </yth-button-legacy>\n                                            <yth-button-legacy variant=\"plain\" onclick=\"javascript:window.history.back();\" href=\"/Search/SearchIndex?c=Jobs&amp;dp=0&amp;sd=Any&amp;sl=Zinniaville,%20Rustenburg,%202999&amp;sli=2062978&amp;ld=5&amp;pn=2&amp;ac=Revert%20to%20search%20results\" theme=\"standard\" size=\"regular\" class=\"hydrated\">Cancel</yth-button-legacy>\n                                    </yth-button-group>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n        </div>\n    ",
