      "details": "\n            \n        <div class=\"card-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"row hmr-6\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 mt-2\">\n                    <h2 class=\"jobtitle mb-1 pb-1\">NYS - Youth Participant - Kwetso Foundation - Modikwe</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <h2 class=\"opportunity-company mb-1 pb-1\">KWETSO FOUNDATION</h2>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col\">\n                        <h5 class=\"opportunity-company mb-1 pb-1 text-grey\">Sponsored by: NYDA Phase 2</h5>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"row verified mb-3 mt-0\">\n                    <div class=\"col\">\n                        <p class=\"verified-text\"><i class=\"icon icon-check2-circle\" style=\"margin-right:2px;\"></i><span>Partner Opportunity</span></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <div class=\"card-detail-meta mt-0\">\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-geo-pin-solid\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Location: </strong>Modikwe, North West</p>\n                            </div>\n\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-calendar-event-solid\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Date posted:</strong> 13 November 2023</p>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-calendar-x\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Closing date:</strong> 31 January 2024 </p>\n                            </div>\n                                <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                    <i class=\"icon icon-cash\"></i>\n                                    <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Salary: </strong>R 1,484.00 per month - Base pay on fixed amount only</p>\n                                </div>\n                            <div class=\"meta-item\">\n                                <i class=\"icon icon-briefcase\"></i>\n                                <p class=\"mb-0\"><strong>Job type: </strong>Paid employment programme</p>\n                            </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col\">\n                    <h6 class=\"opportunity-reference mb-3 mt-3\">Reference number: 1231381</h6>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card-detail-body\">\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"col text-break\">\n                            <h2>Role description</h2>\n                            <p class=\"text-break white-space-pre-line\"></p><p>As a National Youth Service Participant, you will be responsible for &nbsp;some of the following :</p>\n<p><strong>WECGEC (We Clean Green our Education &amp; Public Service Centers Programme) will:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete various community clean-up drives.</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Revitalize &amp; Repair Community Centers, Libraries,&nbsp; Parks &amp; Clinics.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Reading Ambassador's will assist School Learners with:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Teaching learners how to read for understanding</li>\n<li>Completing homework and assignments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Participants will work 2 days a week from 7am to 3pm.</p>\n<p><strong>*This opportunity has 2 roles, namely Team Leaders and Team Members</strong></p><p></p>\n                            <h2>Role requirement</h2>\n                            <p class=\"text-break white-space-pre-line\"></p><p>Applicants Must:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Be Unemployed</li>\n<li>Be 18 - 35 years of age</li>\n<li>Be a South African Citizen with a valid SA ID/Temporary ID.</li>\n<li>Have completed a minimum of Grade 9.</li>\n<li>Have less than 1 year of work - experience.</li>\n<li>Not be currently completing any studies.</li>\n<li>Must be willing to participate in <strong>ANY</strong> of the 2 Positions Mentioned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Individuals living with disabilities are encouraged to apply.</strong></p>\n<p>If living with disability, medical certificate confirming the nature of disability must be provided.</p><p></p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <hr>\n                                \n        </div>\n    ",
